partnerDetails.about: Online Electrical was established in 2004 and is an electrical supply company which has emerged from a group of dedicated people who felt there was a need for a service driven electrical supplier within the local market and those outside of our borders. Our staff has been handpicked for their knowledge in both the electrical and tooling industries and wil be ale to offer both the correct products and advice.
